    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A gruelling first-person exploration game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Delve Deep, Ascend High.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To progress you must explore The Tower over three separate levels, The Underground Dungeons, The Industrial City and The Dark Palace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is made up from many different locations which change each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Queen and Her Heresies.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demented skeletons roam the halls and dungeons, fight your way through them using your war-hammer, crossbow and an assortment of spells, Live long enough and you might encounter The Queen or her heretical abominations.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Starve The Curse.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The land is cursed! Merely being here is enough to ruin you, death is inevitable. The curse can be starved off with potions and blessings, Slaying the demented will also crawl back the hourglass giving you back your precious minutes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sink or Swim?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is dark and unwelcoming, You will fail repeatedly but in doing so you will gain the knowledge to make it further next time.</p>",
